<br>
Perhaps Zellis' idea is good for our server.  Alternatively, to allow for more than one scheduled raid a week, we could extend his plan a bit further to include:<br>
<br>
Wednesday, Saturday - Reservable.<br>
Tuesday, Friday - off limits.<br>
Monday, Thursday, Sunday - FCFS.<br>
<br>
This pleases both sides of the argument, allowing for scheduled raids and spur of the moment raids as well.  As far as respecting the off-limit days, I think the wrath of the Rants board would effectively prevent many transgressions as it has for every other reservable area.  <br>
<br>
My only question is how difficult this will be to moderate.  I'd think it'd be fairly simple, but perhaps Zestrenocya can shed some light. <p>Ganon Stormwynd <BR>
Guild Leader<BR>
