<BR><A HREF="http://www.krunch.net/spiritslammer">Clan Spiritslammer</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvumil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vumil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Lich</span><br>  Posts: 859<br> <font color=#CC9900>(2/6/01 10:23:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: PoG - Easy Solution</span><hr size=1> It's a 30 hour spawn, you waste it 1/2 the time if you schedule every other day.  I guarantee every raid will not clear the zone, and it will take them along time to do so anyways.  So, basically you want to waste limited resources by only allowing people to go there 1/2 the time. <p><br><font face="Arial" size="-2">Vumil Darksoul<br>
